room_title: Escape room "The Ritual Room" by EscapeOut Folsom in Sacramento
room_description:
You awake in an unfamiliar place, with no recollection of how you got here. As your eyes adjust, you feel a deep sense of foreboding… Welcome to the headquarters of the Vox Aurea Society! You and a small group of like-minded citizens have been chosen as possible candidates to join our Secret Society.
However, you must prove you are worthy before being admitted to the inner sanctum. Solve our secrets, and your world will open to luxuries of power and influence beyond your imagination. Fail, and you have seen too much…You have one hour!
